<L>__{interior salieri's apartment dusk 1790's}
<A>__{the d minor concerto continues. salieri, alone, eagerly opens the box from the costume shop and takes out the same dark cloak and hat that leopold wore to the masquerade, only now attached to the hat is a dark mask whose mouth is cut into a frown, not a laugh. it presents a bitter and menacing expression. he puts on the cloak, the hat and the mask and turns his back. suddenly we see the assembled and alarming image reflected in a full length mirror. the music swells darkly.}
